Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.87,0:00:03.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kak Monica.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.33,0:00:05.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari pergi ke festival di Corlapton!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.91,0:00:10.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Corlapton?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.56,0:00:14.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada festival untuk mengiring arwah\Ndi kota sisi timur akademi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.03,0:00:16.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Arwah?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.25,0:00:19.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di sana, ada sebuah legenda.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.37,0:00:23.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Di malam festival, ada penjaga alam baka\Nyang diam-diam membolos
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.15,0:00:27.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}untuk pergi ke festival karena iri pada manusia\Nyang bersenang-senang.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.24,0:00:29.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Alhasil, arwah orang yang sudah meninggal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.85,0:00:33.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}menyelinap dari celah gerbang\Ndan kembali ke dunia nyata."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.17,0:00:37.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat festival itu selesai,\Npengawas dan para arwah akan pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.34,0:00:38.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maka dari itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.10,0:00:41.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kita memakai kostum dan mendentingkan lonceng\Nuntuk mengantar mereka pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.15,0:00:44.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ma-Maaf...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.91,0:00:48.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ada urusan setelah ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.60,0:00:51.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga, aku lupa Kak Monica punya misi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.80,0:00:53.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.45,0:00:56.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lain kali.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.01,0:00:59.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika di Kerbeck ada sebuah festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.55,0:01:03.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku ingin ke sana bersama Nona Isabelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.94,0:01:08.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja. Dengan senang hati!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:11.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat itu, aku akan menjamu dirimu\Ndengan seluruh kemampuanku!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.58,0:02:46.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.92,0:02:51.14,tanda-6,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\fad(550,650)\blur0\bord3\shad0\pos(1824,892)\c&HF5F5F5&\3c&H221A24&\b1}#12  Monica Jadi Anak Nakal
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.52,0:02:48.79,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Waw. Cocok, kok. Cocok.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.79,0:02:50.63,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, kau mau ke mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.67,0:02:51.64,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.15,0:03:00.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku datang untuk menjemputmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.40,0:03:04.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang, aku akan mengantarmu\Nke kediaman Nyonya "Penyihir Pembaca Bintang".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.35,0:03:13.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah, sudah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.65,0:03:16.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian santai saja, tidak perlu setegang itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.94,0:03:20.19,tanda_srt,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"PENYIHIR PEMBACA BINTANG"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.94,0:03:20.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dik Monica, apa kau suka anggur?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.19,0:03:23.89,tanda_srt,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"MARY HARVEY"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.19,0:03:23.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku punya anggur yang bagus dari Farfolia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.98,0:03:25.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.37,0:03:27.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yakin?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.80,0:03:30.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, segelas jus saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.65,0:03:36.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin mengakrabkan diri\Ndengan sesama rekan Tujuh Arif.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.31,0:03:41.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin semakin akrab denganmu, Dik Monica.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.31,0:03:43.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tahu, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.81,0:03:47.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di antara Tujuh Arif lain,\Nhanya kita berdua yang perempuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.98,0:03:52.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Penyihir Pembaca Bintang, Mary Harvey"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.76,0:03:55.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}diperkirakan sebagai Tujuh Arif tertua
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.78,0:03:59.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sekaligus peramal paling hebat di negeri ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.41,0:04:01.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sama seperti Monica\Nyang ahli dalam sihir tanpa mantra
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.11,0:04:04.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan Louis yang ahli dalam sihir pelindung,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.93,0:04:08.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mary Harvey ahli dalam sihir meramal bintang.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.55,0:04:10.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beliau dipercaya oleh Baginda Raja,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.93,0:04:15.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan kebanyakan menjadi pemimpin rapat Tujuh Arif.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.95,0:04:19.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, aku jarang menghadiri rapat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.69,0:04:21.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan masalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.21,0:04:25.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dik Louis dan Dik Emanuel\Nsibuk menyindir satu sama lain,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:28.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dik Raul asyik menyantap sayur-mayur,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:31.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sementara Dik Bradford\Nselalu mendengkur sampai akhir rapat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.65,0:04:35.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sementara itu,\NDik Ray lebih jarang hadir lagi dari Dik Monica.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.70,0:04:39.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lo-Louis sering datang ke tempat ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.64,0:04:40.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.89,0:04:44.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hari ini, Nyonya "Penyihir Pembaca Bintang"\Nmeminta bantuanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.85,0:04:46.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar, untuk melepas sebuah segel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.24,0:04:50.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan melakukan persembahan sihir\Nuntuk melepas partikel sihir di sebuah festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.41,0:04:54.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, ya. Dik Monica juga harus lihat, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.60,0:04:56.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh, itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.11,0:05:00.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Persembahan sihir\Nadalah salah satu kewajiban Tujuh Arif.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.78,0:05:03.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tidak akan rugi kalau menonton untuk belajar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.85,0:05:06.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau Louis?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.75,0:05:09.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak akan ke sana,\Ntapi kalian boleh pinjam Ryn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:12.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia bisa antar kalian ke sana dengan cepat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.47,0:05:14.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah, aku sangat terbantu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.81,0:05:18.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Andai saja Dik Louis lebih muda 15 tahun,\Naku pasti akan mengecup pipimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.87,0:05:24.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Corlapton.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.66,0:05:27.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu festival yang Nona Isabelle sebutkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.71,0:05:29.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, aku sampai lupa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.41,0:05:33.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih sudah bantu\Nmenghitung rekaman observasi siswaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.95,0:05:35.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, bukan masalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:39.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bisa fokus menghitung\Ndi gubuk di tengah gunung.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.58,0:05:45.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau tidak salah, ada satu rekaman observasi\Nyang tercatat sejak 10 tahun lalu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.45,0:05:47.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu bintang milik siapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:51.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pangeran kedua, Yang Mulia Felix Arc Ridill.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.31,0:05:59.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semenjak satu dekade lalu,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.77,0:06:04.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}hanya takdir milik\NYang Mulia Felix-lah yang tidak bisa aku baca.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.05,0:06:11.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, aku akan merias wajah dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.00,0:06:13.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dik Louis juga santai saja di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.18,0:06:22.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku agak cemas soal takdir pangeran kedua\Nyang tidak bisa dibaca.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.58,0:06:23.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setuju.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:26.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan gunakan segala cara untuk membuat
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.18,0:06:30.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}penyusup turnamen catur\Nsebutkan dalang di balik kasus itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.37,0:06:33.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada satu hal yang membuatku\Npenasaran pada penyusup itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.15,0:06:48.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kau menikmati hedonisme liar ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.01,0:06:52.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan ucapkan kalimat itu di depan istriku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.78,0:06:53.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.65,0:06:56.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan melapor pada Nyonya Rosalie
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.30,0:07:00.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bahwa Tuan Louis pergi minum-minum
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.15,0:07:01.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan menggoda banyak pria tampan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:06.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pelayan Payah, kau ingin aku ajari\Ntata krama saat berbicara dari awal, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:10.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebelum itu, aku punya pekerjaan untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.05,0:07:14.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Antarkan mereka berdua ke Corplaton.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.05,0:07:18.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah itu, tolong temani Nona "Penyihir Sunyi".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.16,0:07:22.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yah, anggap saja liburan\Ndan coba nikmati festivalnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.14,0:07:27.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terlebih, persembahan sihir kali ini\Ndigelar dengan alat sihir kuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.71,0:07:31.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau suka yang seperti itu, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:34.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Alat sihir kuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.25,0:07:36.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebuah aksesori yang bisa menyerap energi magis
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.16,0:07:39.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dari dalam tanah,\Nnamanya "Mira Sang Penenun Bintang".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.84,0:07:44.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku dipanggil untuk melepas segel Mira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.26,0:07:47.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yah, melepas segelnya\Nbukan sesuatu yang sulit, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.91,0:07:52.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tahu bahwa alat sihir kuno\Nbisa berpikir sendiri, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.53,0:07:55.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya. Ia punya sejenis kepribadian, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.97,0:07:59.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika pemilik "Mira\NSang Penenun Bintang" itu seorang lelaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.57,0:08:01.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}maka ia akan menjadi alat sihir bermasalah
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.55,0:08:04.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang bisa membunuh pemiliknya sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.94,0:08:10.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat sedang melepaskan segelnya,\Nia selalu berbicara padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.41,0:08:13.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kepribadiannya benar-benar liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.77,0:08:15.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:18.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasanya seperti kesehatan mentalku ikut terkikis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.71,0:08:24.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Alat sihir kuno yang bisa memengaruhi\NTuan Louis yang mentalnya sekuat baja?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.14,0:08:26.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah, aku sampai tertarik.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.20,0:08:28.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau juga punya kepribadian\Nyang membuatku sakit kepala,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:30.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi dalam artian yang lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.98,0:08:36.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan langsung pulang untuk menenangkan hati.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:40.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, aku ingin segera bertemu Rosalie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:51.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa tidak laku juga, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.05,0:08:54.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Andai saja Moses tidak tertangkap,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.37,0:08:56.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mungkin aku tidak perlu kabur sampai sejauh ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.98,0:09:01.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah ada firasat buruk saat dia menyuruhku
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.75,0:09:04.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}menggambar sesuatu\Nyang mirip simbol Perusahaan Abott,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.25,0:09:08.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tidak kusangka dia berusaha\Nmenyusup ke Akademi Serendia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.18,0:09:14.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau tidak salah,\Naku lupa menggambar ekor bantengnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.03,0:09:19.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pokoknya, aku harus segera siapkan uangnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.18,0:09:23.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau sudah seperti ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:27.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebaiknya aku mencuri\Nalat sihir kuno untuk persembahan sihir...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.67,0:09:29.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, ayo coba itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.63,0:09:33.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, aku akan buat replikanya\Ndan jual yang banyak!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.85,0:09:36.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau aku buat dengan kualitas yang asal-asalan,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.26,0:09:38.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku tidak akan ditangkap dan divonis apa-apa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:41.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rupanya aku lumayan pintar juga!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.01,0:09:48.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Permisi, seberapa besar skala energi magis\Nyang bisa diserap "Mira Sang Penenun Bintang"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.11,0:09:50.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pertanyaan bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.29,0:09:53.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika posisi bintangnya bagus,\Nmungkin setara dua, atau tiga kota?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.49,0:09:54.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebanyak itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.09,0:10:02.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya, energi magis yang diserap oleh Mira\Nbisa diubah menjadi sihir ofensif.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.16,0:10:05.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Se-Sepertinya itu rahasia penting, deh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.35,0:10:10.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan masalah, dong? Karena kau Tujuh Arif.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.11,0:10:17.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nah, mari masuk ke dalam gereja.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.11,0:10:19.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ba-Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.00,0:10:39.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya-Yang... Ya-Ya-Yang Mu...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.38,0:10:41.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm? Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.68,0:10:43.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}I-Itu, ada kenalanku...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:46.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Aku ingin memberi salam dulu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.25,0:10:59.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ti-Tidak bisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.54,0:11:03.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak akan bisa menemukan\NYang Mulia di kerumunan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.68,0:11:07.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ups. Unyil, kau baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.31,0:11:11.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Apa kau terluka?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.93,0:11:13.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada sakit di sebelah mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.48,0:11:18.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bu-Bukan. Aku tidak terluka.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.42,0:11:21.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.39,0:11:26.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tersesat, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.43,0:11:30.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bu-Bukan tersesat,\Ntapi aku sedang mencari seseorang.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.71,0:11:35.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa boleh buat. Aku akan bantu cari orang itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.78,0:11:41.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak bisa tenang\Nsetelah melihat gadis seumuranmu menangis.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.45,0:11:44.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namaku Bartholomeus.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:49.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang Ridill mungkin menyebut aku\NBartholomew. Keren, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.62,0:12:08.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kampung halamanku juga punya\Nfestival yang mirip dengan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.65,0:12:12.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lonceng untuk mengantar orang\Nyang sudah meninggal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.15,0:12:16.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tradisi yang indah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.11,0:12:24.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bunyi yang cantik, tapi juga menyedihkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.49,0:12:28.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berapa banyak orang
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.57,0:12:32.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang sempat berpamitan\Ndengan orang yang mereka sayang?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.31,0:12:35.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.71,0:12:38.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga, aku sampai lupa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.31,0:12:40.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sedang mencari orang, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.31,0:12:41.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan jauh-jauh dariku, Unyil.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:43.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ba-Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.01,0:12:45.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Halo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.55,0:12:47.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata kau ada di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.63,0:12:48.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya-Yaya... Ya-Yang...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.95,0:12:53.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia orang yang kau cari?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.81,0:12:56.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih sudah menjaganya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.13,0:12:58.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Santai. Bukan masalah, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.15,0:13:00.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Unyil, jangan sampai terpisah lagi, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.55,0:13:05.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal aku bermaksud diam-diam mengawalnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.15,0:13:08.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}I-Itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.78,0:13:11.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa Yang Mulia ada di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:12.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lihat aku dan coba tebak.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.31,0:13:20.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang Mulia terlihat menikmati festival ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.43,0:13:21.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tepat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.98,0:13:25.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa Yang Mulia Pangeran\Ntidak membawa pengawal bersamanya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.39,0:13:27.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sendiri bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.31,0:13:29.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ke sini dengan siapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.75,0:13:32.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.40,0:13:35.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak ditemani siapa-siapa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.51,0:13:38.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pergi main ke kota ini sendirian?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.70,0:13:40.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.40,0:13:44.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya,\Naku menyembunyikan sesuatu dari Yang Mulia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.79,0:13:48.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.24,0:13:52.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku anak nakal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.25,0:13:58.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ja-Jadi, aku yang nakal ini
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.11,0:14:00.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}pergi main sendirian saat malam hari!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.45,0:14:05.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anak nakal... Kau? Anak nakal?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.38,0:14:08.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oke, berarti kau sama denganku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.06,0:14:10.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita sama-sama anak nakal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.21,0:14:13.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Be-Benar. Sama-sama anak nakal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.03,0:14:14.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku punya saran.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.38,0:14:17.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebagai sesama anak nakal,\Nmau main bersama malam ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.75,0:14:21.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan senang hati!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.15,0:14:27.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah. Panggil aku Ike hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.90,0:14:29.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tu-Tuan Ike?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.41,0:14:34.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan "Tuan Ike", Ike saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.25,0:14:38.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita sesama anak nakal, 'kan? Monica.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.29,0:14:44.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berbuat baik membuat hatiku terasa lebih ringan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:48.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada yang berjaga, dong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.98,0:14:51.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin karena aku tumben-tumbennya berbuat baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.71,0:14:55.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Alat sihir kuno memang beda.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:14:58.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jiwa pengrajinku sampai tersulut!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.63,0:15:10.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sedang meniru bunyi ayam?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.75,0:15:12.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tempat ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.05,0:15:15.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mansion Madam Cassandra.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.98,0:15:18.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuanku!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.60,0:15:20.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Halo, Doris!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.34,0:15:22.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ada perlu dengan Madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.01,0:15:29.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Madam, ada pria tampan\Nyang sudah lama tidak datang menemuimu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.51,0:15:38.75,tanda_srt,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"PEMILIK MANSION, MADAM CASSANDRA"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.51,0:15:38.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Walah, walah. Tuanku, lama tidak berjumpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.31,0:15:43.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hari ini, aku ingin kau siapkan baju untuknya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.51,0:15:45.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, ternyata begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.50,0:15:47.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serahkan saja padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.27,0:15:48.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh? Sebentar...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.28,0:15:58.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini dari bangsawan kenalanmu di toko ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.15,0:16:01.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih untuk semuanya, Madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.35,0:16:11.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka diam-diam menjelekkan\NDuke Clockford dari belakang, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.98,0:16:14.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak bermaksud menyelidiki identitasmu,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.95,0:16:18.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi kau tidak akan bisa datang ke sini lagi, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.16,0:16:27.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Silakan gunakan uang ini\Nuntuk adakan pesta meriah
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.00,0:16:31.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang cocok untuk malam dentingan lonceng\Nyang mengantar arwah mereka yang sudah tiada.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.21,0:16:35.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Madam, Madam!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.95,0:16:39.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}41, 43, 47...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.61,0:16:42.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- 53, 59, 61, 67,\N- Kukira kau berniat menjual gadis itu pada kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.81,0:16:46.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- 71, 73, 77...\N- Maaf, sepertinya kalimatku kurang jelas.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.31,0:16:47.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tujuh puluh sembilan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.10,0:16:51.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bantalan kaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.31,0:16:55.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah kembali ke dunia nyata?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.30,0:16:57.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nah, sekarang penampilanmu
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.21,0:16:59.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sudah sempurna untuk merayakan festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.05,0:17:00.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:04.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuping kuda, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.71,0:17:09.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anak tupai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.34,0:17:10.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, anak tupai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.55,0:17:14.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Malam cepat sekali berlalu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.24,0:17:17.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari kita bermain sepuasnya malam ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.65,0:17:25.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.58,0:17:32.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pegang yang erat,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.49,0:17:34.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}supaya kau tidak terpisah dariku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:37.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Aku akan usahakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.51,0:17:39.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan yang di sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.12,0:17:41.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau beli gelang untuk gadis yang manis itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.07,0:17:44.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh lihat-lihat dulu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.15,0:17:47.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami punya barang spesial, lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.11,0:17:49.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada berkat yang diberikan\Nseorang penyihir ternama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.24,0:17:52.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah. Alat sihir, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.09,0:17:54.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, kurang lebih.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.95,0:17:57.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semuanya tidak punya efek apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.35,0:17:59.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, tapi ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.85,0:18:02.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sihir pelindung sederhana.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.34,0:18:04.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona punya selera yang bagus, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.01,0:18:07.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang yang membuat bros ini adalah
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.31,0:18:10.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}salah seorang Tujuh Arif,\NTuan "Penyihir Permata"!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.69,0:18:11.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.95,0:18:15.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Penyihir Permata", Emanuel Darwin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.95,0:18:18.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kudengar beliau sangat pandai\Nmenciptakan alat sihir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.71,0:18:21.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan tahu banyak, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.35,0:18:23.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh lihat bros itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.15,0:18:30.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mirip dengan bros milik Tuan Cyril.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.11,0:18:33.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seharusnya, bros itu juga memiliki ukiran
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.84,0:18:37.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bertuliskan nama "Penyihir Permata".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.65,0:18:40.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, aku suka. Aku beli bros ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.56,0:18:42.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.01,0:18:47.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Monica, ingin beli sesuatu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.19,0:18:48.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.97,0:18:51.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau merias diri saat turnamen catur, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.00,0:18:56.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa aku boleh hadiahkan aksesori\Nyang cocok dengan riasanmu waktu itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.57,0:19:02.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau masih ingat hari pertama kita bertemu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.70,0:19:03.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di taman lama.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.51,0:19:07.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau menjatuhkan buah kenari.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.91,0:19:12.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat itu, aku merasa amat sangat senang
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.98,0:19:15.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}karena kau memungut buah kenariku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.71,0:19:23.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sudah seperti harta karun untukku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.15,0:19:28.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin aku tidak bisa ungkapkan dengan baik,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.35,0:19:32.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi membeli aksesori dari tempat seperti ini
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.56,0:19:38.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tidak akan sama berkesannya\Ndengan buah kenari itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.95,0:19:43.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.66,0:19:49.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Be-Begini, aku hanya pemula\Nyang baru tertarik merias diri belakangan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.60,0:19:53.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}I-Itu artinya aksesori\Nmasih menjadi tembok yang tinggi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.31,0:19:57.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya! Aksesori itu termasuk item\Nuntuk veteran soal fesyen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.18,0:20:00.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku masih terlalu cepat memakai itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.25,0:20:07.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oke, deh. Aku percaya saja ucapanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.31,0:20:10.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini camilan tradisional\Nfestival dentingan lonceng.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.95,0:20:13.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ia disantap setelah dibagi menjadi dua.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.60,0:20:15.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.01,0:20:17.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mau terima yang ini, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.71,0:20:34.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada yang menempel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.01,0:20:43.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau takut pada orang lain?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.11,0:20:52.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi-lagi... Aku mengabaikan kebaikan orang lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.01,0:20:54.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oke. Begini saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.11,0:20:59.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau anggap aku hantu saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.58,0:21:03.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini malam festival dentingan lonceng
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.61,0:21:06.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang didatangi banyak arwah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.78,0:21:17.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Temanmu, Ike,\Nsebenarnya hantu yang tidak pernah ada.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.81,0:21:21.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena itu, aku tidak akan menyakitimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.25,0:21:37.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Agak haus, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.01,0:21:40.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku beli jus dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.55,0:21:48.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apakah ini situasi "jangan ganggu perempuanku"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.62,0:21:49.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ryn?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.83,0:21:52.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bu-Bukan, dia Yang Mulia Pangeran.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.17,0:21:53.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.75,0:21:59.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berarti, kau sedang mengawal Yang Mulia Felix.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.21,0:22:00.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Be-Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.21,0:22:03.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.25,0:22:05.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.18,0:22:10.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia roh pendamping milik\NNyonya "Penyihir Pembaca Bintang".
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.37,0:22:15.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Ada apa, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.95,0:22:19.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada yang mencuri "Mira Sang Penenun Bintang".
